//http://stackoverflow.com/questions/15154644/group-by-to-combine-concat-a-column
//GROUP BY to combine/concat a column

#input

ID,  User,  Activity,  PageURL 
 1,  Me,    act1,      ab     
 2,  Me,    act1,      cd     
 3,  You,   act2,      xy     
 4,  You,   act2,      st

#output

User,  Activity,  PageURL  
Me,    act1,      ab cd     
You,   act2,      xy st

# constraint
{
	"constants": [ ],
	"aggregation_functions": ["concat"]
}

# solution

```sql
SELECT
    User,
    max(Activity),
    string_agg(PageURL, ' ') 
FROM
    input1 
GROUP BY
    User 
ORDER BY
    User ASC
```
